profile:
Your deck is an extension of your living space... a place to unwind and entertain. Precision Deck and fence is here to make your dream outdoor living space become a reality. 

Our priority is not to meet expectations, but to exceed them. Our customers keep coming back because we’re dependable, knowledgeable and pleasant to work with.

Precision Deck and Fence aims to provide quality craftsmanship that you can rely on. We take the time and care to make sure even the tiniest detail is managed, in every circumstance. There really is no other way.

We are committed to making our services personal. In keeping with this desire, we’re not satisfied with our work until you are.

Reach out to us today -  Call or text 519-377-8130, or send us an email bnrred@gmail.com. It would be our pleasure to serve you!
